    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy. The exterior shows heavy wear, including several deep scratches, dents, and visible rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells. Inside, the upholstery is torn in multiple places, and the electronics are inconsistent. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and the transmission shifts harshly, suggesting it needs immediate professional attention. This is a project car for someone willing to invest time and parts into a full restoration.",
