    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super clean on the inside and runs like a dream! It\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready for its next big adventure. If you\u2019re looking for something reliable that looks great without the 'brand new' price tag, this is the one for you. Come swing by and take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re gonna love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) features the robust 3.6L M96 flat-six with VarioCam Plus, delivering linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut with upgraded Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, while the factory-spec limited-slip differential ensures optimal corner-exit traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a new water pump. While the Arctic Silver finish shows light patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical integrity and throttle response are sharp. A driver-focused example with exceptional mid-range torque and communicative hydraulic steering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
