      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between daily reliability and pride of ownership. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor road nicks expected of a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the leather seats remain supple and free of tears, and every button and dial functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, it is sound, having undergone regular fluid changes and preventative maintenance. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts with precision. Recent tire replacements and a fresh professional detail make this car ready for its next owner to drive away with total confidence.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
